c: 24
v: 22
t: "Abeeyisa obulungi mu ddiini era abagaziyizibwa mu byenfuna tebalayiranga obutawa ab'oluganda olw'okumpi n'abanaku n'abaasenguka olw'okuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda. Basaana basonyiwe era balekere, abaffe (mmwe) temwagala Katonda kubasonyiwa era nga bulijjo Katonda musonyiyi musaasizi"